Package: MTVGARCH
Type: Package
Title: Smooth Transition Modelling of GARCH Processes with Time-Varying Variance
Version: 0.9.1.21
Author: Glen Wade
Maintainer: The package maintainer <glenpwade@gmail.com>
Description: MTVGARCH is multiplicative object describing both the Garch process and a time-varying variance (tv) component.
    Support is provided for univariate and multivariate models.  Methods for estimation and testing are included.
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: True
Depends: methods
Imports: stats,doParallel,Matrix,foreach
